{
  "info": {
    "name": "Same Day Solution — Payout Partner API",
    "description": "Bank payout (IMPS/NEFT) for B2B partners — powered by **Same Day Solution Pvt. Ltd.** and SparkUpTech Express Pay.\n\nUse this collection to move money from your **partner wallet** to a **vendor's bank account**. Your wallet balance is debited for each transfer.\n\n## Authentication\nEvery authenticated request requires 3 headers:\n- `x-api-key` — Your public API key\n- `x-signature` — HMAC-SHA256 signature\n- `x-timestamp` — Current Unix timestamp (ms)\n\nSignature formula:\n```\nHMAC_SHA256(api_secret, JSON.stringify(body) + timestamp)\n```\nFor GET requests (no body): `HMAC_SHA256(api_secret, '' + timestamp)`\n\n## Setup\n1. Set `api_key` and `api_secret` in Collection Variables\n2. Pre-request scripts auto-generate the signature\n3. Run **Get My Balance** to check your wallet balance\n4. Run **Get Bank List** → **Verify Bank Account** → **Initiate Transfer** → **Get Transfer Status**\n\n## Partner Wallet\nAdmin credits your partner wallet. Each payout debits your wallet balance directly — no merchant_id required.\n\n## Security\n- IP whitelisting enforced (contact admin to whitelist your server IP)\n- Timestamp tolerance: 5 minutes\n- HTTPS required in production\n- API key permission required: `payout` or `all`\n\n## ⚠️ Postman Cloud Agent\nIf you see **\"IP address not authorized\"** even though your IP is whitelisted, the request may be going through Postman's cloud servers.\n\n**Fix:** Postman **Settings → General** → turn **OFF** **\"Send requests through Postman's cloud agent\"** (or use the Postman desktop agent) so requests use your real IP.\n\n## Capabilities\n- Check wallet balance\n- Bank list (IMPS/NEFT filters)\n- Verify bank account (beneficiary name; no penny drop charge)\n- Initiate transfer (debits your partner wallet: amount + charges)\n- Poll status by `transactionId` or `clientRefId`, or list your last 20 payouts\n\n## Duplicate prevention\nA second transfer to the **same account number** within **2 minutes** while a prior attempt is still pending/processing/success returns **429** with `wait_seconds` (remaining time in that window).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "version": "3.0.0"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "noauth"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "https://api.samedaysolution.in", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "api_key", "value": "pk_live_YOUR_API_KEY_HERE", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "api_secret", "value": "sk_live_YOUR_API_SECRET_HERE", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "last_payout_transaction_id", "value": "YOUR_TXN_UUID", "type": "string", "description": "Internal payout row UUID. Initiate Transfer (test) saves this on 200; replace manually if needed." }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔐 Payout — Authenticated",
      "description": "All requests require `x-api-key`, `x-signature`, and `x-timestamp` headers.\n\nThe pre-request script automatically calculates the HMAC signature.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get My Balance",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const CryptoJS = require('crypto-js');",
                  "let apiKey = pm.collectionVariables.get('api_key');",
                  "let apiSecret = pm.collectionVariables.get('api_secret');",
                  "if (!apiKey) apiKey = pm.environment.get('api_key');",
                  "if (!apiSecret) apiSecret = pm.environment.get('api_secret');",
                  "const placeholderKey = 'pk_live_YOUR_API_KEY_HERE';",
                  "const placeholderSecret = 'sk_live_YOUR_API_SECRET_HERE';",
                  "if (!apiKey || apiKey.trim() === '' || apiKey === placeholderKey) { throw new Error('Set api_key in Collection Variables (or Environment).'); }",
                  "if (!apiSecret || apiSecret.trim() === '' || apiSecret === placeholderSecret) { throw new Error('Set api_secret in Collection Variables (or Environment).'); }",
                  "const timestamp = Date.now().toString();",
                  "const signature = CryptoJS.HmacSHA256('' + timestamp, apiSecret).toString(CryptoJS.enc.Hex);",
                  "pm.request.headers.upsert({ key: 'x-api-key', value: apiKey });",
                  "pm.request.headers.upsert({ key: 'x-signature', value: signature });",
                  "pm.request.headers.upsert({ key: 'x-timestamp', value: timestamp });"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status is 200', function() { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.test('Has balance', function() { pm.expect(j.success).to.be.true; pm.expect(j.balance).to.be.a('number'); });",
                  "  console.log('Partner wallet balance: ₹' + j.balance);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "x-api-key", "value": "{{api_key}}" },
              { "key": "x-signature", "value": "auto-generated" },
              { "key": "x-timestamp", "value": "auto-generated" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/partner/payout/balance",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "partner", "payout", "balance"]
            },
            "description": "Returns your partner wallet balance.\n\nThis balance is debited when you call **Initiate Transfer**.\n\nIf balance is 0, contact Same Day admin to top up your wallet."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 — Balance",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"balance\": 50000.00,\n  \"is_frozen\": false,\n  \"freeze_reason\": null,\n  \"last_updated\": \"2026-04-10T10:00:00.000Z\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "200 — Wallet Frozen",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"balance\": 10000.00,\n  \"is_frozen\": true,\n  \"freeze_reason\": \"Pending verification\",\n  \"last_updated\": \"2026-04-10T10:00:00.000Z\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
